com.vernalis.knime.mmp

Class FragmentKeyMorganFP

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.knime.mmp.FragmentKey
      • com.vernalis.knime.mmp.DefaultFragmentKeyFingerprinted
        • com.vernalis.knime.mmp.FragmentKeyMorganFP
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FragmentKeyFingerprinted, java.lang.Comparable<FragmentKey>

    public class FragmentKeyMorganFP
extends DefaultFragmentKeyFingerprinted
    This class extends the FragmentKey class, adding a Morgan fingerprint rooted at each attachment point. It will still appear to function if attachment points were not tracked during fragmentation, but the results will not be meaningful.
    Author:
    Steve Roughley
